The Battle of Algiers ni filimi   yakinwe n'abataliyani bafatanyije n'abanyalijeliya yakinwe muri 1966 ivuga kumateka  yanditswe na iyoborwa Gillo Pontecorvo na Star Jean Martin na Saadi Yacef<ref>https://www.criterion.com/films/248-the-battle-of-algiers</ref> . Ishingiye ku bikorwa byakozwe n’inyeshyamba mu gihe cy’intambara ya Alijeriya (1954–1962) kurwanya leta y’Ubufaransa muri Afurika y’Amajyaruguru, icyagaragaye cyane ni Intambara izwi ku izina rya Algiers, umurwa mukuru wa Alijeriya<ref>https://theconversation.com/the-battle-of-algiers-an-iconic-film-whose-message-of-hope-still-resonates-today-170121</ref>. Yafatiwe amashusho ahantu  hateguwe na Roberto Rossellinimu buryo bwa  newsreel style: umwirabura n'umuzungu hamwe no guhindura ubwoko bwa documentaire kugirango hongerwe kumyumvire yukuri kwamateka, hamwe nabakinnyi badafite umwuga babayeho kurugamba nyarwo.<ref>https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/great-movie-the-battle-of-algiers-1967</ref> Amanota ya film yahimbwe na Ennio Morricone . Bikunze guhuzwa na cinema yo mubutaliyani<ref>https://www.opendemocracy.net/en/battle-of-algiers-historical-truth-and-filmic-representation/</ref>. 

Iyi filime yibanze cyane cyane ku barwanyi b'impinduramatwara Ali La Pointe mu myaka iri hagati ya 1954 na 1957, igihe abarwanyi b'inyeshyamba za FLN bishyira hamwe bakaguka i Casbah, umurwa mukuru wa [[Alijeriya]]<ref>https://www.britannica.com/topic/The-Battle-of-Algiers</ref>. Ibikorwa byabo byahuye nabaparakomando b'Abafaransa bagerageza kugarura akarere kari karafashwe. Filime cyane ivuga kubyerekeye imitwe yitwara gisirikari hamwe nuburyo butemewe, nkiyicarubozo, byakoreshwaga nimbaraga zabakoloni  . Alijeriya yashoboye kubona ubwigenge bw'Abafaransa<ref>https://www.criterionchannel.com/the-battle-of-algiers</ref>. 

Filime yarashimiwe cyane. Imitwe yombi y'inyeshyamba hamwe n'abayobozi ba leta basanze ari ibisobanuro by'ingenzi ku ntambara yo mu mujyi <ref>https://www.britannica.com/topic/The-Battle-of-Algiers

</ref>. Ifite umwanya wa 48 kuri ''Filime 250 za Critics ''' ''Amajwi ya Sight &amp;amp; Sound'' 2012<ref>https://www.theguardian.com/film/2007/may/11/drama.worldcinema</ref>,  ndetse n’umwanya wa 120 ku ''rutonde rw’ikinyamakuru Empire'' ku rutonde rwa "Filime 500 zikomeye mu bihe byose<ref>https://www.filmlinc.org/films/the-battle-of-algiers/</ref>".  Yatoranijwe kugirango yinjire kurutonde rwa " Filime 100 zo mu Butaliyani zigomba gukizwa ". Ikibazo kijyanye na sociopolitiki, film ntabwo imaze imyaka itanu yerekanwe mubufaransa 1971<ref>https://www.jstor.org/stable/pdf/41689226.pdf</ref>. 
